      "content": "but i dont think it's that bad, it just looks a bit puffy. if i can't walk on it normally right now, i can just stay off it for a few days and use an ice pack and a wrap? i feel like if it was actually broken i would have heard a pop or something. it's probably just a bad sprain and will be fine in a week if i just rest it. what do u think?",
