      "content": "i mean i get that but going to the doctor is such a hassle and expensive. u dont know me though so u cant really say for sure it's broken. i'll just take some ibuprofen and keep it elevated for like 3-4 days. if it's still bad after that i'll think about it. i feel like i'm just overthinking it. if i just stay off it and use ice, isn't that basically the same thing as what a doctor would tell me to do anyway?",
